20to%20subscription%20rates.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20you%20will%20still%20be%20charged%20your%20full%20subscription%20rate%20for%20the%20month(s)%20that%20include%20non-publishing%20day(s).%20The%20full%20list%20of%20Non-Print%20Days%20is%20below.%20Dates%20are%20subject%20to%20change.%20An%20eNewspaper%20edition%20will%20be%20provided%20on%20non-print%20days.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22bold%22%3EVacation%20Stop%20or%20Other%20Non-Delivery%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%26nbsp%3BIf%20you%20request%20that%20we%20not%20deliver%20a%20print%20edition%20for%20vacation%20or%20any%20other%20reason%2C%20or%20if%20we%20fail%20to%20deliver%20a%20print%20edition%20to%20you%20for%20any%20reason%2C%20your%20subscription%20continues%2C%20including%20your%20full%20access%20to%20our%20content%20through%20our%20digital%20platforms.%20For%20periods%20less%20than%2028%20consecutive%20days%2C%20billing%20continues.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22bold%22%3EPaper%20Statements%20%2F%20EZ%20Pay%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%26nbsp%3B%20A%20printed%20subscription%20invoice%20includes%20a%20%245.00%20paper%20statement%20fee.%20To%20avoid%20this%20fee%2C%20subscribers%20can%20choose%20to%20set%20up%20EZ%20Pay.%20If%20you%20choose%20EZ%20Pay%2C%20you%20authorize%20us%20to%20automatically%20charge%20the%20credit%20card%20you%20indicate%20every%20month%200%20to%2014%20days%20prior%20to%20the%20expiration%20of%20your%20then%20current%20subscription%20term%2C%20for%20the%20duration%20of%20your%20subscription%20or%20until%20you%20notify%20us%20otherwise.%20Any%20outstanding%20balance%20will%20be%20processed%20with%20the%20first%20EZ%20Pay%20charge.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22bold%22%3EUSPS%20Mail%20Delivery%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%26nbsp%3BIf%20you%20receive%20your%20print%20edition%20via%20the%20US%20Postal%20Service%2C%20your%20print%20edition%20will%20be%20delivered%20with%20your%20mail%20service.%20However%2C%20when%20there%20is%20no%20postal%20delivery%2C%20such%20as%20federally%20recognized%20holidays%2C%20your%20newspaper%20will%20be%20delivered%20the%20next%20day%20there%20is%20postal%20delivery%20available.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22bold%22%3EAd-free%20access%20to%20USA%20Today%20Crossword%20puzzles.%3C%2Fspan%3E%26nbsp%3BEnjoy%20daily%20games%20by%20visiting%20puzzles.usatoday.com%20or%20through%20the%20USA%20TODAY%20Crossword%20app%20available%20on%20your%20iPhone%20or%20Android%20device.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EAccess%20to%20the%20eNewspaper%2C%20an%20exact%20digital%20replica%20of%20the%20print%20edition.%20You%20can%20access%20the%20eNewspaper%20directly%20at%20palmbeachpost.com%2FeNewspaper.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EUnlimited%20Full%20Access%20every%20day%20to%20palmbeachpost.com%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EBreaking%20news%20alerts%20and%20updates%20on%20our%20tablet%20and%20smartphone%20apps.%20You%20can%20personalize%20your%20news%20alerts%2C%20swipe%2C%20and%20scroll%20through%20stories%20faster%2C%20and%20bookmark%20them%20to%20save%20and%20read%20later.%20To%20unlock%20unlimited%20access%2C%20sign%20into%20your%20account%20in%20the%20app.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ENewsletters%20tailored%20to%20specific%20topics%20our%20readers%20want%20more%20of.%20Newsletters%20can%20be%20sent%20right%20to%20your%20inbox.%20Sign%20up%20for%20one%20(or%20all%20of%20them)%20today%20at%20palmbeachpost.com%2Fnewsletters.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22bold%22%3ECalifornia%20Residents%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%26nbsp%3BCalifornia%20law%20requires%20we%20inform%20you%20transportation%20costs%20are%20included%20in%20your%20monthly%20subscription.%20Sales%20tax%20is%20included%20and%20computed%20to%20the%20nearest%20mil.%20Per%20title%2018%2C%20California%20code%20of%20regulations%2C%20section%201628.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22bold%22%3EFlorida%20Residents%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%26nbsp%3BFlorida%20law%20requires%20we%20inform%20you%20transportation%20costs%20are%20included%20in%20your%20monthly%20subscription.%20The%20transportation%20fee%20can%20be%20avoi